-- Spanish Police Arrest Youth Planning ‘Columbine-Style’ Killing
-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 2012-10-04T16:38:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-04/spanish-police-arrest-youth-planning-columbine-style-killing.html
Spanish police yesterday arrested a
21-year-old youth planning to imitate the killings at Columbine
High School in the U.S. in 1999 by setting up bombs on the
campus of the Balearic Islands University, according to a
 statement  released today by the  Interior Ministry .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Angeline Benoit in Madrid at 
